        </picture>

        <p class="ChristmasIntro-text">Come one, come all as Generic Church hosts A Christmas Spectacular, an entirely-free experience for the whole family! Come enjoy the holiday cheer throughout Santa's workshop, as you learn what it takes to be one of Santa's elves. See below for event times and a location near you.</p>

